	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello<br /><br />Here is an small game I began a little while back , and recently &quot;wrapped it up&quot;.  The game is meant to be played with the famicom mic, but can be also played in a NES with the joystick. ( &quot;can be played&quot; is in both cases pretty speculative because I had not yet the chance to test it on hardware. By the way, if somebody can confirm that works in real life, I will be very grateful <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />  )<br /><br />Features music by <a href="http://www.surasshu-sound.com/" class="postlink">Surasshu</a> who did an awesome job.<br /><br />The concept is based on a famicase entry: <a href="http://famicase.com/11/softs/41.html" class="postlink">(this one)</a><br /><br />Messy source included inside the archive: (Now moved to itch.io)<br /><a href="http://zurashu.itch.io/utaco" class="postlink">うたいたガールUTACO~「ＩＩコンは世界を救う？！」</a>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


